headline: Kinder Morgan Remains A Good, But Not Great, Play
summary: Kinder Morgan forecasts 2025 adjusted EPS of $1.27 and EBITDA of $8.3 billion, driven by natural gas operations. Find out why I think KMI stock remains a buy.
